panels.description: Status timeline of Light Sensor Status, Shutter Status, and StartUp.

targets.query: SELECT last("LIGHT_SENSOR_STATUS") FROM "$quabo" WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)
SELECT last("SHUTTER_STATUS") FROM "$quabo" WHERE  "observatory" = '$observatory' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)
SELECT last("StartUp") FROM $quabo WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)
